creator: Vekelz Technology
descriptionHtml:
Vekelz aims to connect cars owners with service centers, no matter the kind of service using the following methods:

- Detect users locations and connect them to the nearest service center.

- Check if service center has specific products like oil, tires, batteries or even have different other services like oil change and more.

- Set route to some point on the map and check if there is any services or products within their route.

- Rate and comment on specific service or product to enhance other users experience.

- Mark car for sale and it will appear in Vekelz cars market.

- Review the history and dates of maintenance of the car before applying for purchase it.

- Create special alerts to notify them of various maintenance dates.
descriptionShort: Vekelz aims to connect cars owners with service centers.
